328
00:28:23,576 --> 00:28:25,995
Semua karena kecelakaan itu!

329
00:28:29,290 --> 00:28:30,166
Kecelakaan?

330
00:28:31,668 --> 00:28:32,585
Detektif...

331
00:28:34,421 --> 00:28:35,422
itu...

332
00:28:45,223 --> 00:28:47,475
Katakan yang kau ketahui!

333
00:28:47,892 --> 00:28:49,477
- Hei!
- Apa maumu?

334
00:29:08,997 --> 00:29:09,873
Hitoshi!

335
00:29:57,295 --> 00:29:59,464
Kenapa? Kenapa kau membunuhnya?

336
00:30:00,465 --> 00:30:01,341
Katakan!

337
00:30:01,966 --> 00:30:03,218
Kenapa kau membunuhnya?

338
00:30:05,345 --> 00:30:06,471
Jawab!

339
00:30:07,055 --> 00:30:08,264
Kubilang jawab!

340
00:30:08,765 --> 00:30:10,558
Sekarang!

341
00:30:14,062 --> 00:30:15,522
Dia tidak bersalah!

342
00:30:16,606 --> 00:30:17,982
Tidak ada yang naik

343
00:30:18,691 --> 00:30:20,235
bus itu!

344
00:30:25,907 --> 00:30:27,617
Jika itu benar,

345
00:30:28,117 --> 00:30:30,286
tidak akan ada korban lainnya!

346
00:30:30,870 --> 00:30:33,665
Itu bukan salahnya!

347
00:30:33,748 --> 00:30:34,666
Diam!

348
00:30:35,583 --> 00:30:36,543
Dengar!

349
