akan kuakhiri sendiri.

358
00:31:39,314 --> 00:31:40,398
- Tidak!
- Hentikan!

359
00:31:48,615 --> 00:31:49,490
Hitoshi!

360
00:31:56,581 --> 00:31:57,874
Kau tidak akan pernah

361
00:31:59,417 --> 00:32:01,044
menangkapku.

362
00:32:07,925 --> 00:32:09,218
Hitoshi!

363
00:32:18,394 --> 00:32:20,521
- Maafkan aku...
- Tidak mau bergerak.

