00:33:29,382 --> 00:33:31,426
Akan kuawasi kau selamanya!

384
00:33:33,803 --> 00:33:34,971
Detektif itu...

385
00:33:37,265 --> 00:33:38,266
Dia...

386
00:33:39,809 --> 00:33:41,644
Ohyama

387
00:33:43,896 --> 00:33:46,190
melakukan itu pada Hitoshi-ku!

388
00:33:48,860 --> 00:33:49,819
Bukankah dia

389
00:33:51,529 --> 00:33:53,573
sudah membayar utangnya?

390
00:33:58,953 --> 00:34:00,371
Dia mencegahnya.

391
00:34:03,249 --> 00:34:04,709
Detektif Ohyama

392
00:34:08,504 --> 00:34:10,590
mencegah terjadinya kejahatan lain.

393
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:13,843
Kami

394
00:34:16,846 --> 00:34:17,847
sejak saat itu

395
00:34:19,140 --> 00:34:20,933
menjalani hidup dengan tenang.

396
00:34:23,519 --> 00:34:24,729
Aku yakin semua orang

397
00:34:26,272 --> 00:34:28,149
sudah lupa tentang insiden itu.

398
00:34:31,652 --> 00:34:34,072
Kenapa kau harus membuka kembali
investigasi itu?

399
00:34:39,535 --> 00:34:41,537
Jika putramu terbunuh, apa kau bisa

400
00:34:43,915 --> 00:34:45,291
begitu saja

401
