menonton film dan tertawa bersama

441
00:39:51,597 --> 00:39:53,724
agar dia bisa menghiburmu.

442
00:39:57,686 --> 00:40:00,439
Ohyama! Akan kubalas kebaikanmu.

443
00:40:03,025 --> 00:40:04,151
Dia...

444
00:40:05,778 --> 00:40:07,780
sangat menantikan

445
00:40:08,697 --> 00:40:10,783
menonton film itu denganmu.

446
00:40:23,754 --> 00:40:24,880
Detektif Ohyama.

447
00:40:27,716 --> 00:40:29,385
Detektif Ohyama, bisa mendengarku?

448
00:40:33,347 --> 00:40:36,600
Kami sudah menangkap
pembunuh berantai Josai.

449
00:40:48,779 --> 00:40:50,364
Kau...

450
00:40:51,407 --> 00:40:53,784
Kau menemukan buktinya?

451
00:40:55,870 --> 00:40:56,954
Kau...

452
00:41:03,002 --> 00:41:03,919
Bukan...

